title: rito pls I just want chest
body: plez i just want chest but wits end nautilus gets it?

replies.body: My Guess is it is because of low CS, even if on Twisted Treeline.
If you want chests easily, play weird offmeta stuff. I have had no trouble getting every one of my chests on the day it recharges, since i figured this out. It is quite amusing.
and or play with friends, since if they get an S you get a chest for it i think.
